nodes.text: A male warrior of Clan Vizsla of House Vizsla pledged his Mandalorian clan to Lady Bo-Katan Kryze and the Mandalorian resistance against the Galactic Empire along with several other Mandalorian factions during the Mandalorian Civil War after she obtained the Darksaber. As a result of the Mandalorian warrior's support for Lady Bo-Katan, she became Mand'alor.
